{
  "texts": [
    "We model molecule description as bidirectional conversions between natural language and SMILES, as well as conversions between natural language.",
    "We model molecule design as a conversion from natural language to SMILES.",
    "We also model product inference and retro-synthesis prediction as conversions from SMILES to SMILES.",
    "Additionally, we have also included a task for yield prediction.",
    "The illustration of our unified modeling between natural language and SMILES."
  ]
}